          "text": "C(9, 7)"
        },
        {
          "key": "D",
          "text": "C(11, 7)"
        }
      ],
      "correctAnswer": "A",
      "explanation": "By symmetry property: C(n,k) = C(n, n-k), so C(10,7) = C(10, 10-7) = C(10,3).",
      "difficulty": "easy"
    },
    {
      "id": "mcq-3",
      "question": "The sum \u03a3 C(n,k) for k=0 to n equals:",
      "options": [
        {
